notes: Drinks:Zimbabwe: 61runs/1wkt, after 15 overs,4ex,7x4 2x6, (Masakadza H 35, Taylor B.11)
Masakadza H:51 runs off 59 balls, in 91 minutes 5x4 2x6
2nd wicket:50 runs off 70 balls, 2ex, in 46 minutes, (Masakadza.H 26, Taylor B. 22)
2nd wicket: 102 runs off 122 balls in 75 minutes,2ex,8x4 1x6( Masakadza H 55, Taylor B. 43)
B.Taylor: 50 runs off 72 balls in 95 minutes, 3x4 0x6
Shapoor cramped again and he is taken of after delivering 4 balls
Drinks: Afghanistan: 111 runs/2 wkts, after 19 overs, 5ex, 12x4 2x6

milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (525) involving teams Zimbabwe & Afghanistan in ODIs
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (36) for AFG, going past Samiullah Shinwari
